        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "If we divide by ∆x, we get ",
          "block_bbox": [
            52,
            418,
            1288,
            527
          ],
          "block_id": 1,
          "block_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_label": "formula",
          "block_content": "\\frac{\\Delta(u v)}{\\Delta x}=u\\frac{\\Delta v}{\\Delta x}+v\\frac{\\Delta u}{\\Delta x}+\\Delta u\\frac{\\Delta v}{\\Delta x}",
          "block_bbox": [
            469,
            616,
            1880,
            852
          ],
          "block_id": 2,
          "block_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "If we now let $\\Delta x\\rightarrow0$ , we get the derivative of uv:",
          "block_bbox": [
            24,
            933,
            2446,
            1049
          ],
          "block_id": 3,
          "block_order": 4
        },
        {
          "block_label": "formula",
          "block_content": "\\begin{aligned}\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(uv\\right)&=\\lim_{\\Delta x\\to0}\\frac{\\Delta(uv)}{\\Delta x}=\\lim_{\\Delta x\\to0}\\left(u\\frac{\\Delta v}{\\Delta x}+v\\frac{\\Delta u}{\\Delta x}+\\Delta u\\frac{\\Delta v}{\\Delta x}\\right)\\\\&=u\\lim_{\\Delta x\\to0}\\frac{\\Delta v}{\\Delta x}+v\\lim_{\\Delta x\\to0}\\frac{\\Delta u}{\\Delta x}+\\left(\\lim_{\\Delta x\\to0}\\Delta u\\right)\\left(\\lim_{\\Delta x\\to0}\\frac{\\Delta v}{\\Delta x}\\right)\\\\&=u\\frac{dv}{dx}+v\\frac{du}{dx}+0\\cdot\\frac{dv}{dx}\\end{aligned}",
          "block_bbox": [
            237,
            1178,
            2816,
            2136
          ],
          "block_id": 4,
          "block_order": 5
        }
      ],
      "markdown": "## The Product Rule \n\nIf we divide by ∆x, we get \n\n$$\\frac{\\Delta(u v)}{\\Delta x}=u\\frac{\\Delta v}{\\Delta x}+v\\frac{\\Delta u}{\\Delta x}+\\Delta u\\frac{\\Delta v}{\\Delta x}$$\n\nIf we now let $\\Delta x\\rightarrow0$ , we get the derivative of uv:\n\n$$\\begin{aligned}\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(uv\\right)&=\\lim_{\\Delta x\\to0}\\frac{\\Delta(uv)}{\\Delta x}=\\lim_{\\Delta x\\to0}\\left(u\\frac{\\Delta v}{\\Delta x}+v\\frac{\\Delta u}{\\Delta x}+\\Delta u\\frac{\\Delta v}{\\Delta x}\\right)\\\\&=u\\lim_{\\Delta x\\to0}\\frac{\\Delta v}{\\Delta x}+v\\lim_{\\Delta x\\to0}\\frac{\\Delta u}{\\Delta x}+\\left(\\lim_{\\Delta x\\to0}\\Delta u\\right)\\left(\\lim_{\\Delta x\\to0}\\frac{\\Delta v}{\\Delta x}\\right)\\\\&=u\\frac{dv}{dx}+v\\frac{du}{dx}+0\\cdot\\frac{dv}{dx}\\end{aligned}$$",
      "tables": [],
      "formulas": [
        {
